Dacomitinib was developed by Pfizer Inc and approved by the FDA on September 27, 2018.[L4810] Some evidence in the literature suggests the therapeutic potential of dacomitinib in the epithelial ovarian cancer model[A39624], although further investigations are needed.', '["L01EB07"]', '[]');
